        <div class='post' itemprop='articleBody'>
          <p>This is a quick and dirty page. I don’t want to spend too much effort on it. It’s very low priority. Even fairly categorizing these projects can open a can of worms - also keep up to date. Better to add any disclaimer on top as required.</p>
<p>Target audience are developers who are researching what kind of projects exist so they can decide which ones to work on or fork as well as advanced users. All of them need to take the information with caution and research independently on their own if the provided information (is still) accurate of if they disagree for some reason.</p>
<p>Blanket disclaimer:<br>
All statements are either false or incomplete.</p>
        </div>

