<blockquote>
<p>Seems like saying “when booting into superadmin delete /home/user first”.</p>
</blockquote>
</aside>
<p>We don’t have local attackers in our threat model. Android does.</p>
<aside class="quote no-group" data-username="Patrick" data-post="35" data-topic="4557">
