</blockquote>
<p>Current model:</p>
<ol>
<li>“the attacker has to compromise the device remotely first to enable OEM unlocking”</li>
<li>“then have physical access to the device to unlock the bootloader which then wipes all user data so they can’t access anything.”</li>
