<blockquote>
<p>It’s your choice to spend your time attacking the project by spreading misinformation and spin about it</p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>You’re trying to misrepresent</p>
</blockquote>
<p>etc.</p>
<p>Newsflash: different people, different opinions.</p>
<p>Are you going to apologize? No.</p>
